Package org.jlab.phaser.swing.generated

package org.jlab.phaser.swing.generated
Provides the classes generated with Netbeans Matisse builder tool. Classes in this package should be edited very carefully and flagged code blocks should be edited with the builder tool. Observe the *.form files.
